Third-Party Notice
==================

This extension's netlist navigation engine (parser, symbol index, and language
providers under `src/`) is derived from the HSPICE IntelliSense extension by
Vladimir Aptekar:

  Name:        HSPICE IntelliSense
  Author:      Vladimir Aptekar
  License:     MIT
  Source:      https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=vladimir-aptekar.hspice-intellisense

The original parser logic was ported and substantially simplified: Spectre
branches, `simulator lang=` switching, the case-sensitivity toggle, and the
language-server process model were removed; HSPICE-only navigation now runs
in-process. `.LIB` dual-syntax handling, `.param` variable navigation, `.LIB
section` scoping, and the multi-definition resolver are original additions not
present in the upstream extension. See the file headers in `src/` for per-file
attribution.
